      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Store and forward (SAF) teledermatology has been found to improve access to dermatologic care; in addition, it can be highly reliable and accurate in the diagnosis and management of dermatologic disease. Here we report a case of a suspected hedgehog dermatosis diagnosed via SAF teledermatology in a young woman."
